INSERT INTO designer (name, bio) VALUES 
('Origin', 'ORIGIN brand, headquartered in Farmington, Maine, was created by BJJWeekly, & co-creator Pete Roberts back in 2009. Pete''s vision was not to create a "fight brand" but instead a BJJ lifestyle brand that spoke directly to the needs of the everyday BJJ enthusuast. As a designer adn entrepreneur, Pete brings 15+ years of branding experience into an industry which he is passionate about growing.'),
('FUJI', 'FUJI Sports (together with Hatashita Sports) was founded in 1969 by Frank Hatashita, 8th Dan. Hatashita Sensei was Vice-President of the IJF (International Judo Federation), and President of the Pan American Judo Federation, among other positions including an IJF referee, and owner of many dojo and affiliates.'),
('War Tribe', 'War Tribe was established to create innovative products made with high-quality materials for the Jiu Jitsu and mixed martial arts (MMA) athlete. We love Jiu Jitsu, we love MMA, and we love participating in the culture and industry we are a part of. What we do is a result of our passion for the art, sport, and lifestyle of the athletes we serve. Every Jiu Jitsu Gi we design is a direct result of our motto and passion. Made with quality materials and built for the athlete, a War Tribe BJJ Gi is always recognizable on the mat. Complete with unique artistic design, our products have become a statement of defiance, but also of benevolence. Our vast artistic Jiu Jitsu Gi collections reflect the true message of our sport.
The War Tribe mission is to elevate the sport and lifestyle of mixed martial arts through our innovative products while promoting the Jiu Jitsu way of life. One who wears War Tribe is born to win, determination is in their blood and inevitable success is in their future.'),
('B-TEAM', 'B-TEAM, comprised of ex DDS (Danahar Death Squad) Members like "Craig Jones", "Nicky Ryan", "Ethan Crelinsten, and "Nicky Rod" bring a different comedic aspect to Jiu Jitsu apparel. Founded in 2022'),
